{"id":5434,"date":"2016-05-01T23:55:46","date_gmt":"2016-05-01T23:55:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/?p=5434"},"modified":"2021-03-01T10:22:11","modified_gmt":"2021-03-01T15:22:11","slug":"7-best-yoga-poses-for-weight-loss","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/7-best-yoga-poses-for-weight-loss\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Best Yoga Poses for Weight Loss"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">When using yoga poses for weight loss, it&#8217;s important to remember that&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">less is more<\/span>.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">That instead of poorly doing all hundreds of&nbsp;yoga poses, you should focus on&nbsp;mastering the&nbsp;<strong>key poses for strength, flexibility, balance, and weight loss.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">A lot of people are also skeptical about <a href=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/use-yoga-for-weight-loss\/\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">how effective yoga can be for&nbsp;weight loss.<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">The facts are that yoga not only burns a similar calorie rate to jogging but that it also&nbsp;<strong>lowers cortisol levels in the body.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Make no mistake &#8211; <strong>you can LOSE your excess weight with the right yoga poses and yoga practice.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">In the following article, we have organized some of the most effective yoga poses for weight loss.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Try these today, and see how you feel&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. Boat Pose<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261341339.jpg\" alt=\"Boat pose - #1 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4954\" title=\"Boat pose - #1 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261341339.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261341339-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261341339-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>This pose is one of the best for working the core. &nbsp;The difficulty lies mainly in keeping the legs AND the back straight &#8211; making a &#8220;V&#8221; shape. &nbsp;This requires a tremendous amount of <a href=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/8-yoga-poses-strong-core\/\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">core strength.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Beginners may need to try it first with the legs bent before progressing because&nbsp;it also requires some <a href=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/get-flexible-fast-yoga\/\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">flexibility<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. Crescent Lunge<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678219.jpg\" alt=\"Crescent Lunge - #2 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4955\" title=\"Crescent Lunge - #2 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678219.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678219-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678219-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Lunges are great because there are so many variations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can bend the back knee or keep it outstretched. &nbsp;The farther you sink down, you more you take the stretch into the hips, which makes this one of the best poses for <a href=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/yoga-poses-beginners-hips\/\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">stretching the hips<\/a> and preparing for splits.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you tilt the arms and hands back, you will take the stretch into your back.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. Four-Limbed Staff Pose<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679164.jpg\" alt=\"Four-Limbed Staff Pose - #3 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4956\" title=\"Four-Limbed Staff Pose - #3 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679164.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679164-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679164-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>This pose makes the list because it&#8217;s also called the &#8220;yogi pushup&#8221; (aka Chaturanga). &nbsp;Do 20 of these in a row from plank position, and you&#8217;ll feel the burn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need more?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Try holding the position for 10-30 seconds. &nbsp;Make sure to keep the back straight and in-line with the upper arms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Warrior III<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678141.jpg\" alt=\"Warrior III - #4 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4957\" title=\"Warrior III - #4 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678141.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678141-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678141-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>What the picture doesn&#8217;t tell you is that this pose requires a LOT of core strength and leg and hip flexibility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s tougher to hold that back leg up than you would think.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Get someone to take a picture of you to check your form. &nbsp;It&#8217;s quite difficult to hold that straight line with the entire body while balancing on one leg. &nbsp;Try holding it for 30 seconds.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. Reverse Plank<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678234.jpg\" alt=\"Reverse Plank - #5 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4958\" title=\"Reverse Plank - #5 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678234.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678234-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260678234-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re tired of the plank (which is still one of the best poses to build heat in the core), try this variation! This pose works the core and shoulders.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The shoulder strength is necessary for all inversions and most advanced poses. &nbsp;Keeping your butt lifted is what makes this pose much harder&nbsp;than it looks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>6. Triangle Pose<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679077.jpg\" alt=\"Triangle Pose - #6 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4959\" title=\"Triangle Pose - #6 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679077.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679077-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_260679077-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll feel this one in the obliques, hamstrings, core, and chest! &nbsp;It&#8217;s one of the most important&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/yoga-asanas-for-weight-loss\/\"  rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">yoga poses for weight loss<\/a> that works multiple muscle groups.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternate sides or between revolved triangle pose (rotate the body so that the other hand touches the same foot that is currently forward in triangle).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>7. Wheel Pose<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261338540.jpg\" alt=\"Wheel Poses - #7 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" class=\"wp-image-4960\" title=\"Wheel Poses - #7 of the yoga poses for weight loss\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261338540.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261338540-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/04\/shutterstock_261338540-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>This pose makes the list because it&#8217;s a little more difficult to hold if you&#8217;re a beginner. &nbsp;The more difficult yoga poses for weight loss will be the ones that will challenge you, help you learn, improve, and burn more fat!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to do some warm-up poses for the back such as cobra, upward facing dog, and camel pose before you jump into wheel pose.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>If you liked these poses for weight loss and are looking for some additional tips and an actual workout plan, our&nbsp;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yogafatlossbible.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Yoga Fat Loss Bible for Beginners<\/a><\/span>&nbsp;is a great place to start.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes with&nbsp;everything you need to get started, including&nbsp;a <strong>complete 6-week workout plan, a flexibility guide, and a beginner&#8217;s guide to meditation!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yogafatlossbible.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"258\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Avocadu-Yoga-Fat-Loss-Bible.png\" alt=\"Avocadu Yoga Fat Loss Bible\" class=\"wp-image-26019\" title=\"Avocadu Yoga Fat Loss Bible\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Avocadu-Yoga-Fat-Loss-Bible.png 600w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Avocadu-Yoga-Fat-Loss-Bible-300x129.png 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Avocadu-Yoga-Fat-Loss-Bible-365x157.png 365w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Avocadu-Yoga-Fat-Loss-Bible-355x153.png 355w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>It\u2019s a&nbsp;great solution around for those looking to<strong> lose weight, get more flexible, and relieve aches and pains<\/strong> with a calm yoga practice.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It will show you exactly how to <strong>melt away stubborn body fat <\/strong>with a regular yoga practice and has the top 50 fat-burning yoga poses every beginner should learn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\"><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/yogafatlossbible.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Click here to check out the Yoga Fat Loss Bible.<\/span><\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Always remember that the&nbsp;most difficult part of doing yoga getting yourself on the mat!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Leave a comment below if you enjoyed this article or have any questions!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>When using yoga poses for weight loss, it&#8217;s important to remember that&nbsp;less is more.&nbsp; That instead of poorly doing all hundreds of&nbsp;yoga poses, you should focus on&nbsp;mastering the&nbsp;key poses for strength, flexibility, balance, and weight loss. A lot of people are also skeptical about how effective yoga can be for&nbsp;weight loss. The facts are that&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":18,"featured_media":31807,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_kad_blocks_custom_css":"","_kad_blocks_head_custom_js":"","_kad_blocks_body_custom_js":"","_kad_blocks_footer_custom_js":"","_kad_post_transparent":"","_kad_post_title":"","_kad_post_layout":"","_kad_post_sidebar_id":"","_kad_post_content_style":"","_kad_post_vertical_padding":"","_kad_post_feature":"","_kad_post_feature_position":"","_kad_post_header":false,"_kad_post_footer":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[25,26],"tags":[],"taxonomy_info":{"category":[{"value":25,"label":"Weight Loss"},{"value":26,"label":"Yoga"}]},"featured_image_src_large":["https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/05\/Best-Yoga-Poses-for-Wei